<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> yaṇa pratāpa cakravartti siṁhaṇadēva <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ya śrāvaṇa bahuḷa 1 maṁgaḷavārada <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> sabhāmaṁṭapadalu mahāsabheyāgi neredirddu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> dhyāyara makkaḷu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> bhaṭṭōpādhyāya <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ge voṁdu gāṇa <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṟa <unclear>koṁ</unclear>ḍu ko <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> keṁdu biṁnaha māḍalu Ā mahājana <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> samasta śrīkāryyakkōsuga <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> māneṁṇneyanu koṭṭaru yī dha <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <note n="263-2">The continuation is lost.</note>
</p>

<p>1) This record is found in continuation of No. 211 above (ARS, IE 1938-39, B.K. No. 53). Since it contains a different date, it has been separately given here as No 53-A.</p>

